remember a number called turn with 0
remember a number called score with 0
remember a string called game-state with playing

when turn is above 0
  show "turn started"

when score is above 50
  remember a string called game-state with winning
  show "you are winning"

when score is above 100
  remember a string called game-state with victory
  show "VICTORY"
  finish

when game-state is equal to winning
  show "keep going"
